'''AGO esports''' is a Polish esports organization.

In the past, they have partnered with [[Team Singularity]], [[Rogue (European Team)|Rogue]], and Alior Bank to form '''[[AGO Singularity]]''', '''[[AGO ROGUE]]''', and '''[[AliorBank Team]]''' respectively, as their ''League of Legends'' division.

